Title: Cornell Nanofabrication Facility Home Page
Body: MIME-Version: 1.0 Server: WebSTAR/1.2.1 ID/28 Message-ID: Date: Sunday, 01-Dec-96 13:21:05 GMT Last-Modified: Thursday, 21-Nov-96 05:23:20 GMT Content-type: text/html Content-length: 3512 Cornell Nanofabrication Facility Home Page The Cornell Nanofabrication Facility (CNF), formerly known as the National Nanofabrication Facility at Cornell University (NNF) and prior to that the National Research and Resource Facility for Submicron Structures (NRRFSS) , has served the US research community for more than 15 years by providing nanofabrication services to over 500 research projects.
